measurements.description: Sixteen well-displayed, slightly cupped flowers on 16 up-to 11-cm inflorescences; plant 47 cm x 18 cm, grown in bark in a 20-cm plastic bulb pan; dorsal sepal upright to reflexed, intense fuchsia, white tips; lateral sepals tending toward porrect, intense fuchsia, white tips; petals full, ovate, slight ruffled margins, intense fuchsia; lip tubular, margin ruffled, intense violet distally, light spot center edge, throat light yellow; column pale green; substance moderate; texture crystalline.
